Nowadays, teenagers are paying more attention to those common problems happening in human's daily life.
I generally agree with this opinion.

Firstly, young generations has more concerned and understanding of the consequences of this kind of problems.
They are also better educated than previous generations and learned from the past how the polluted environment, poverty, animal extinction.
Due to the advancement of the technology and media plays a big role in making aware about these topics.
They are more in touch about these issuses and capable to do with this relevance as to what happen in the surroundings.